Item.value: Workflow for processing a Change Request Revision.
Notify the CR Requestor & Analyst the CR was approved for implementation.

WorkflowTemplate.name: Change Review Board (CRB): Review Proposed Solution

Item.value: Change Review Board (CRB): Review Proposed Solution and make a cost benefit business decision.
Choose signoff team.
CRB makes a cost-benefit business decision. - Approve - continue to implement the change - Reject - the Change Specialist will determine the intended disposition - record signoff comments
The Change Review Board (CRB) participant assignments are checked and if empty the user is prompted to assign them.
Task checks if Change Review Board (CRB) is assigned and if not routes the workflow to a task requesting its assignment.
Assign the Change Review Board (CRB) participants on the CR revision. The CRB will review the Proposed Solution. Complete task when assignment done.
This task sets the CR revision's fast track field.
Is enough information available to go to the CRB? Does the CR fit the Fast Track criteria? Please complete these fields: - Fast Track - Technical Review Priority - Reason

WorkflowTemplate.name: Analyst: Identify Impacted Items, Propose Solution, Estimate Cost

Item.value: Perform impact analysis and propose a solution. Please complete these fields: - Proposed Solution - Recurring Cost - Nonrecurring Cost - Technical Recommendation - Test Results Attached - Technical Recommendation Date - Timing Factors
The Change Specialist 1 & Analyst participant assignments are checked and if empty the user is prompted to assign them.
Task checks if Change Specialist 1 is assigned and if not routes the workflow to a task requesting its assignment.
Assign the Change Specialist 1 participant on the CR revision. Complete task when assignment done.

Assign the Analyst participant on the CR revision. If additional users to the Analyst also need to add inputs, then assign them to the Change Contributors participant. Complete task when assignment(s) done.
Task checks if Analyst is assigned and if not routes the workflow to a task requesting its assignment.
Task sets the CR revision's Disposition to Investigate.

WorkflowTemplate.name: Specialist: Set Change Review Board Decision

Item.value:
Set the Change Review Board intended decision. Review signoff comments. Poll the CRB members or convene a meeting.
Please complete these fields: - Timing Factors
